New () Syntax In Place! It's Pretty!

More complex query parsing, removing 'and'

We've removed 'and' and have broken parsing the query out into its own function. This was done to allow for () syntax. There are a bunch of special cases in place to make syntax sugar for users.

use native min and max functions
